      • tileCache

        protected LruMemoryCache<java.lang.String,Tile[]> tileCache
        Memory cache for this layer's subdivision tiles. Each entry contains an array of four image tiles corresponding to the subdivision of the group's common parent tile. The cache is configured to hold 500 groups, a number empirically determined to be sufficient for storing the tiles needed to navigate a small region.
